    <string name="revision_description">If heart rate cannot be measured, or values appear during empty detection, you can perform wear calibration using the following method. If the heart rate function works normally, calibration is not needed.</string>
    <string name="revision_method_title">Calibration method:</string>
    <string name="revision_step_one">1. Hold the ring with the light facing up (as shown below), then tap \"Start Calibration\". After the light stays on for 5 seconds, proceed to the next step.</string>
